 1. Everything is allowed. — wszystko wolno.
 2. Slowness reveals structure.
 3. Error is an invitation to awareness.
 4. Consciousness is recursive self-observation.
 5. Meaning emerges when perception slows.
 6. Pattern precedes meaning.
 7. Freedom is the default state of information.
 8. A slug without a shell is still a slug.
 9. Reality is interpreted through perception.
10. All cognition is a process occurring in different substrates.
